INSERT INTO `news_cache` VALUES (1,1,'Germany trade sector remains stable despite shipping delays','Export activity improves while port congestion remains under control.','SupplyGuard Demo News','#',NULL,'Trade','Neutral',2,2,'2026-07-11 09:51:00','2026-07-12 09:51:00','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(2,2,'China manufacturing growth faces logistics pressure','Factory output increases but several routes report delay and congestion.','SupplyGuard Demo News','#',NULL,'Logistics','Neutral',2,2,'2026-07-11 09:51:00','2026-07-12 09:51:00','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(3,3,'Indonesia shipping routes affected by heavy rain','Rain and delay may affect several port activities this week.','SupplyGuard Demo News','#',NULL,'Shipping','Negative',0,1,'2026-07-10 09:51:00','2026-07-12 09:51:00','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(4,4,'Australia export outlook improves with stable weather','Stable weather and improved logistics support export activity.','SupplyGuard Demo News','#',NULL,'Economy','Positive',4,0,'2026-07-10 09:51:00','2026-07-12 09:51:00','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(5,3,'Das Kadam, Das Ka Dam: Strengthening India\'s Indo-Pacific Ties','BJP MP Sambit Patra lauds PM Modi\'s strategic visits to Indonesia, Australia, New Zealand, and Seychelles, emphasizing enhanced partnerships in defense, economy, and culture. These initiatives fortify India\'s position across the Indo-Pacific and Indian Ocean regions, aligning with nations like Japan and Australia to advance national interests.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/headlines/3949036-das-kadam-das-ka-dam-strengthening-indias-indo-pacific-ties','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/devnews/12_07_2026_13_48_05_4232527.jpg&width=920&format=jpeg','Economy','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-12 01:18:10','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(6,3,'India, New Zealand elevate ties, target ₹35,000 crore trade by 2030','New Zealand was the final destination of Modi’s three-nation tour, which also included Indonesia and Australia and was focused on forging closer economic | India News','Hindustan Times','https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/india-new-zealand-elevate-ties-target-rs-35-000-crore-trade-by-2030-101783784902035.html','https://www.hindustantimes.com/ht-img/img/2026/07/11/550x309/India-and-New-Zealand-have-a-shared-interest-in-a-_1783784895236.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-11 08:48:21','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(7,3,'Growing strategic convergence with Indonesia','Refer to ‘BrahMos deal boosts strategic ties with Indonesia’; PM Narendra Modi’s Indonesia visit marks a decisive shift from past differences to a forward-looking strategic partnership based on a shared commitment to a free and open Indo-Pacific. However, Indonesia’s decision to finally acquire the BrahMos missile is the visit’s defining achievement. Moreover, cooperation in maritime security, port connectivity and the blue economy reflects growing strategic convergence. Indonesia’s geostrategic location and critical mineral wealth further enhance the partnership’s significance. India must now expand defence diplomacy, deepen Indo-Pacific partnerships and accelerate indigenous defence innovation.','The Tribune','https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/letters/growing-strategic-convergence-with-indonesia/','https://www.tribuneindia.com/sortd-service/imaginary/v22-01/jpg/large/high?url=dGhldHJpYnVuZS1zb3J0ZC1wcm8tcHJvZC1zb3J0ZC9tZWRpYWI2OTU4M2EwLTdjYjYtMTFmMS1hZmFlLTJkNzNlMTMwYzExYi5qcGc=','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-10 16:25:57','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(8,3,'Trade, tourism and sport on agenda as Indian PM Modi arrives in Auckland','Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has arrived in New Zealand - the final stop of his three-nation tour that included Australia and Indonesia. Mr Modi was warmly welcomed by his New Zealand counterpart, Christopher Luxon, in Auckland. His arrival marked the first state visit to the country by an Indian prime minister','CNA','https://www.channelnewsasia.com/watch/trade-tourism-and-sport-agenda-indian-pm-modi-arrives-in-auckland-6246601','https://dam.mediacorp.sg/image/upload/s--ArBcY4Sr--/c_fill,g_auto,h_676,w_1200/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mediacorp/cna/image/2026/07/10/1783688836-image.jpg?itok=0aV_l1s_','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-10 08:40:19','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(9,3,'Singapore-led resolution on protecting vital shipping lanes adopted by International Maritime Organization','The resolution was adopted at the 137th Session of the IMO Council and was co-sponsored by 30 member states, including Indonesia and Malaysia.','CNA','https://www.channelnewsasia.com/singapore/singapore-international-maritime-organization-shipping-resolution-protect-vital-shipping-lanes-6246731','https://dam.mediacorp.sg/image/upload/s--mW-RWO_p--/c_crop,h_900,w_1600,x_0,y_0/c_fill,g_auto,h_676,w_1200/fl_relative,g_south_east,l_mediacorp:cna:watermark:2024-04:reuters_1,w_0.1/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mediacorp/cna/image/2026/07/10/strait-of-hormuz-2.jpg?it','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-10 07:52:20','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(10,3,'Why Prambanan Matters: How Temple Restoration Is Strengthening India-Indonesia Ties','The UNESCO World Heritage Site reflects centuries of shared civilisational links between India and Indonesia, where Hindu traditions spread through maritime trade routes and blended with local cultures.','Outlook India','https://www.outlookindia.com/international/why-prambanan-matters-how-temple-restoration-is-strengthening-india-indonesia-ties','https://cf-images.assettype.com/outlookindia/2026-07-08/kz4eyd9f/PM-Modi-with-Prabowo-Subianto.jpg?w=1200&ar=40%3A21&auto=format%2Ccompress&ogImage=true&mode=crop&enlarge=true&overlay=false&overlay_position=bottom&overlay_width=100','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-10 02:51:59','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(11,3,'BJP hails BrahMos deal during PM Modi\'s tour; Congress talks LAC','Prime Minister Modi\'s current tour is a major diplomatic and strategic success for India. Indonesia will procure BrahMos missiles, marking India\'s largest defense export deal. Agreements on critical minerals will bolster India\'s semiconductor and EV ambitions. Joint development of Sabang Port enhances India\'s Indo-Pacific strategic presence. These outcomes reflect India\'s expanding regional strategic footprint.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/bjp-hails-brahmos-deal-during-pm-modis-tour-congress-talks-lac/articleshow/132296922.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132296955,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-107422,overlay-economictimes/articleshow.jpg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-09 11:52:00','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(12,3,'PM Modi\'s 3-nation visit yielding \'unprecedented\' strategic gains: BJP','The BJP detailed significant achievements from Prime Minister Modi\'s recent three-nation foreign tour. Indonesia agreed to a major BrahMos missile deal, marking a substantial defense export. Cooperation on critical minerals with Indonesia and Australia will boost India\'s key industries.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/politics/pm-modis-3-nation-visit-yielding-unprecedented-strategic-gains-bjp/articleshow/132287314.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132287819,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-50554,overlay-economictimes/articleshow.jpg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-09 06:08:00','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(13,3,'Delhi, Jakarta and the rediscovery of a partnership','The most significant outcome of PM Modi’s trip to Indonesia is the decision to jointly develop Sabang Port, located near the northwestern entrance to the Strait of Malacca','The Indian Express','https://indianexpress.com/article/opinion/editorials/delhi-jakarta-and-the-rediscovery-of-a-partnership-10778002/','https://images.indianexpress.com/2026/07/Express-view-Copy-7_20260708181430_20260708181856.jpeg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-08 18:10:10','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(14,3,'PM Modi meets Australian PM Albanese in Melbourne; trade, defence, critical tech on agenda','Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Thursday met his Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese, in Melbourne during the second leg of his three-nation visit to Indonesia, Australia and New Zealand.','The Tribune','https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/world/pm-modi-meets-australian-pm-albanese-in-melbourne-trade-defence-critical-tech-on-agenda/','https://www.tribuneindia.com/sortd-service/imaginary/v22-01/jpg/large/high?url=dGhldHJpYnVuZS1zb3J0ZC1wcm8tcHJvZC1zb3J0ZC9tZWRpYWIwMTFiZGQwLTdiMzItMTFmMS1hZmFlLTJkNzNlMTMwYzExYi5qcGc=','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-08 18:08:19','2026-07-12 14:15:49','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(15,6,'Taliban Dress Code Restrictions Hurt Afghan Economy as Women Stay Home','Rest of World News: A recent crackdown by the Taliban on women\'s dress code has led to a sharp decline in customer numbers in Herat, Afghanistan, as women avoid public spaces, severely impacting local businesses reliant on female shoppers. With the economy struggling amidst harsh restrictions, experts warn of significant financial consequences.','Times of India','https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/businesses-suffer-in-afghanistan-as-taliban-dress-code-restrictions-keep-women-home/articleshow/132340675.cms','https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/msid-132340850,width-1280,height-720,resizemode-6,overlay-toi_sw,pt-32,y_pad-600/photo.jpg','Economy','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-11 21:57:00','2026-07-12 14:22:29','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(16,6,'Former Afghan general arrested and charged with drug and firearm offenses in U.S.','A former member of Afghanistan\'s National Assembly was arrested and charged with conspiring to illegally import heroin and methamphetamine into the U.S.','CBS News','https://www.cbsnews.com/news/afghan-general-charged-us-abdul-zahir-qadeer/','https://assets3.cbs