nt both to the knockout round of the World Cup.','WTOP','https://wtop.com/sports/2026/06/austria-and-algeria-draw-3-3-at-world-cup-to-advance-to-knockout-round-and-send-iranians-home/','https://wtop.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Austria_Algeria_WCup_Soccer_73614-scaled.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-27 22:07:53','2026-07-12 14:22:37','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(29,67,'Austria, Algeria trade goals, both advance at World Cup','Austria, Algeria trade goals in stoppage time, both advance at World Cup with stunning 3-3 draw at end of group stage.','Boston.com','https://www.boston.com/sports/world-cup/2026/06/28/austria-algeria-trade-goals-in-stoppage-time-both-advance-at-world-cup-with-stunning-3-3-draw/','https://bdc2020.o0bc.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Austria_Algeria_WCup_Soccer_73614-6a40a1acdde83-768x432.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-27 22:07:53','2026-07-12 14:22:37','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(30,67,'Austria, Algeria trade goals in stoppage time, both advance at World Cup with stunning 3-3 draw','Marko Arnautovic and Marcel Sabitzer also had goals for Austria, which finished second behind Argentina in Group J to advance for the first time since 1982 | Football News','Hindustan Times','https://www.hindustantimes.com/sports/football/austria-algeria-trade-goals-in-stoppage-time-both-advance-at-world-cup-with-stunning-3-3-draw-101782620944170.html','https://www.hindustantimes.com/ht-img/img/2026/06/28/550x309/austria_1782621008384_1782621008517_9da69181-1cb1-4ba6-850a-b396d90fb366.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-27 21:32:44','2026-07-12 14:22:37','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(31,67,'Austria, Algeria trade goals in stoppage time, both advance at World Cup with stunning 3-3 draw','Austria and Algeria played to a thrilling draw in what amounted to a win-win result in their World Cup group-stage finale, allowing both to advance to the knockout round while eliminating Iran.','SFGATE','https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/austria-and-algeria-draw-3-3-at-world-cup-to-2