trikes-drone-threats-and-hormuz-closure-2946012-2026-07-12','https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202607/iran-strikes-kuwait-095243155-16x9.jpg?VersionId=s23JtP1X_qt9jI57i3NGNR9XpkRH5TSy','Logistics','Negative',0,1,'2026-07-11 21:46:44','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(88,27,'US-Iran news LIVE: Hegseth says Tehran will ‘pay’ as US strikes energy hubs; sirens sound in UAE, Bahrain','US-Iran news LIVE: The US carried out its third round of strikes on Iran this week, targeting facilities linked to Tehran’s ability to threaten commercial shipping in the Gulf. | World News','Hindustan Times','https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/us-iran-news-live-updates-trump-tehran-strait-of-hormuz-closed-irgc-khamenei-strikes-uae-bahrain-kuwait-oil-prices-101783824834682.html','https://www.hindustantimes.com/ht-img/img/2026/07/12/550x309/logo/trump_war_iran_1783825671126_1783825687383_846ddc2a-f8a0-4f88-9561-d88f6827d719.png','Logistics','Negative',0,2,'2026-07-11 20:38:21','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(89,27,'US-Iran War Live: No Iran deal if we don\'t get the nuclear dust, says senior US officials','US-Iran War Live Updates: The US and Iran exchanged fresh military strikes, deepening their direct confrontation and pushing a fragile three-week-old ceasefire closer to collapse. Iran retaliated by launching missiles and drones at US military infrastructure in Bahrain, Kuwait, Qatar and Jordan after Washington carried out another wave of strikes on Iranian targets, saying the operation was aimed at protecting commercial shipping through the Strait of Hormuz. Tehran accused the US of interfering in the strategic waterway and warned that any further intervention would draw a \"crushing response\", insisting the strait would reopen only under Iranian supervision. The escalation unfolded as Iran buried slain Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei at the Shrine of Imam Reza in Mashhad, where thousands of mourners carrying Iranian flags and portraits of the late leader gathered for his funeral, with some displaying banners reading \"We Will Kill Trump\". Iranian officials said recent US strikes killed 14 people and wounded 78 across five provinces, while fresh explosions were reported in Bushehr and Bandar Abbas, including near the perimeter of Iran\'s only operational nuclear power plant. Kuwait said it intercepted missiles and drones targeting US military assets, while Jordan reported shooting down several incoming missiles. Qatar condemned attacks on commercial shipping but urged all sides to return to diplomacy, as Turkey and Oman also called for restraint in separate talks with Iranian Foreign Minister Abbas Araqchi. Stay with IndiaToday.in for the latest updates.','India Today','https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/us-iran-war-live-updates-strait-of-hormuz-middle-east-tensions-ceasefire-donald-trump-west-asia-crisis-2944508-2026-07-10','https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/breaking_news/202607/trump--mojtaba--us-iran-103059965-16x9_0.png?VersionId=OHn3ksecjTFkCIQXW7TaNQbyXnB2n6iV','Logistics','Negative',0,5,'2026-07-09 11:47:16','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(90,27,'Bahrain has not used UAE swap, in talks over F1 race, minister says','Bahrain\'s economy is expected to contract by 3% this year due to the ongoing conflict with Iran, according to S&P Global, amidst a fiscal deficit of nearly 8.5% of GDP.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/business/3947858-bahrain-has-not-used-uae-swap-in-talks-over-f1-race-minister-says','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/imagegallery/29_02_2020_19_14_39_2122985.jpg&width=920&format=jpeg','Weather','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-09 05:24:39','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(91,27,'US and Iran exchange intensifying fire across the Mideast, threatening the interim deal to end war','United States forces launched new airstrikes against Iran early Thursday. Tehran responded by targeting U.S.-allied Mideast countries in an exchange of fire. Sirens sounded in Bahrain, Kuwait, Qatar, and Jordan amid the escalating conflict. U.S. President Donald Trump warned of further escalation if shipping attacks continue. These events threaten an interim deal intended to end the war in the region.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/us-and-iran-exchange-intensifying-fire-across-the-mideast-threatening-the-interim-deal-to-end-war/articleshow/132285238.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132285370,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-183532,overlay-etdefence/articleshow.jpg','Logistics','Negative',0,2,'2026-07-09 04:30:00','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(92,27,'US airstrikes on Iran spur Gulf missile alerts, putting ceasefire at risk','The United States launched fresh strikes across Iran as Tehran targeted Bahrain, Kuwait and Qatar. The exchange has shaken the ceasefire and revived fears over Hormuz shipping and a wider regional war.','India Today','https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/us-airstrikes-iran-gulf-missile-alerts-hormuz-ceasefire-risk-ptag-2944019-2026-07-09','https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202607/pti-international-1-original_72-sixteen_nine.png?VersionId=VDZlwIAX.GxOWzxvPoH7fk7NM6pKRrMs','Logistics','Negative',0,2,'2026-07-09 02:48:32','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(93,27,'US military carries out fresh strikes on Iran, prompting Iran attacks on Kuwait and Bahrain','By Humeyra Pamuk, Gram Slattery and Tala RamadanANKARA/DUBAI, July 8 (Reuters) - The U.S. military said on Wednesday it launched fresh strikes on Iran to keep the Strait of Hormuz open to shipping, triggering Iranian attacks on Kuwait and Bahrain in the latest escalation to derail efforts to end the war.The latest round of attacks, which the U.S. said was carried out in response to Tuesday\'s assault on three cargo ships transiting the strait, came hours after President Donald Trump said he believed an interim ceasefire with Iran to be \"over.\"','Al-Monitor','https://www.al-monitor.com/originals/2026/07/us-military-carries-out-fresh-strikes-iran-prompting-iran-attacks-kuwait-and','https://www.al-monitor.com/sites/default/files/styles/social_media_share/public/2026-07/2026-07-08T042831Z_2_LYNXMPEM6705P_RTROPTP_4_IRAN-CRISIS.JPG?h=4462e40b&itok=QnRMh_mP','Logistics','Negative',0,3,'2026-07-09 01:58:18','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(94,27,'US strikes 90 Iran targets as Tehran retaliates across Gulf','The United States launched fresh strikes across Iran after attacks on shipping and military sites. Iran hit Bahrain, Kuwait and Qatar in response, pushing the fragile Gulf ceasefire closer to collapse.','India Today','https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/us-iran-conflict-us-strikes-iran-tehran-hits-bahrain-kuwait-qatar-ptag-2943797-2026-07-09','https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202607/pti-international-2-original_68-sixteen_nine.png?VersionId=1hi5od0e9UbNcooYVq4Wlu1YC1qzxhcH','Logistics','Negative',0,2,'2026-07-08 21:04:26','2026-07-12 14:24:33','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(95,27,'Iran targets Kuwait, Bahrain as US launches fresh strikes on Tehran','US strikes on Iran to secure the Strait of Hormuz followed Iranian attacks on Kuwait and Bahrain, derailing peace efforts and pushing oil prices up..Strait of Hormuz, US military strikes Iran, Iran attacks Kuwait Bahrain, Freedom of navigation, Middle East conflict, Donald Trump Iran, Ceasefire with Iran, Commercial shipping attacks, International waterway security, Iran\'s leverage negotiations, Oil prices Brent crude, Bandar Abbas strikes, Chabahar power outage, Iran nuclear doctrine, UN Security Council Iran','Malayala Manorama','https://www.onmanorama.com/news/world/2026/07/09/us-strikes-iran-attacks-kuwait-bahrain.html','https://img.onmanorama.com/content/dam/mm/en/archive/news/world/images/2026/5/2/donald-trump.jpg','Logistics','Negative',0,4,'2026-07-08 20:44:08','2