siness leaders as part of preparations for implementing the trade pact. He is also scheduled to meet EU Trade Commissioner Maros Sefcovic in Brussels. \"We have already started marketing Indian goods and services so that we are future-ready to get the best out of the FTAs that we have finalised,\" Goyal said at an event organised by the Council for Leather Exports.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/india-eu-aim-to-complete-fta-legal-scrubbing-in-15-20-days-says-piyush-goyal/articleshow/132227911.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132225003,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-586147,overlay-etmarkets/articleshow.jpg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-06 12:13:00','2026-07-12 14:25:47','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(123,33,'Díaz-Canel announces economic reforms to attract investment and involve Cubans abroad','Cuban President Miguel Díaz-Canel has announced economic reforms to attract investment and involve Cubans abroad in the economy. He has emphasized the need for change, stating the country can\'t continue on its current path. The announcement comes amid a severe economic crisis with power outages and shortages. The U.S. tightened oil supply restrictions in January, worsening the situation. Díaz-Canel suggests eliminating state intermediaries in trade and offering tariff benefits for raw materials. Meanwhile, humanitarian aid from Colombia, Mexico and Belize has arrived, providing essential goods as the U.S. energy embargo persists.','The Atlanta Journal-Constitution','https://www.ajc.com/news/2026/06/diaz-canel-announces-economic-reforms-to-attract-investment-and-involve-cubans-abroad/','https://images.ajc.com/resizer/v2/OF2AZDB2YBEGHPD4STZHN2X2QQ.jpg?auth=db442a50cfedffef4016ed66e381ba5e5d09342ddc05a62b2ab5282dcf9bf9e0&width=1200&height=630&smart=true','Trade','Negative',0,1,'2026-06-12 11:53:37','2026-07-12 14:25:50','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(124,23,'WTO and OIF Report Highlights Digital Trade\'s Growth Potential','Titled Dig