d US Trade Tensions','Tariffs imposed by the Trump administration on Brazilian goods are impacting Brazil\'s sugar industry, especially in the northeast. Trump\'s proposals for higher tariffs threaten access to the U.S. market. The northeast, supplying most of Brazil\'s U.S. sugar quota, is poised to feel the sting of decreased exports.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/business/3946791-tariffs-squeeze-brazils-sugar-industry-amid-us-trade-tensions','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/aiimagegallery/26_09_2025_01_09_08_6802713.png&width=920&format=jpeg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-07 12:24:52','2026-07-12 14:27:54','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(155,37,'Brazil\'s Senator Bolsonaro argues against 25% US tariff on its exports','Brazilian Senator and presidential hopeful Flavio Bolsonaro on Tuesday argued to the U.S. Trade Representative (USTR) against a new 25% tariff on Brazilian goods, distancing ​himself from a policy that had been used as a cudgel to ‌defend his father.','Reuters','https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazils-senator-bolsonaro-argues-against-25-us-tariff-its-exports-2026-07-07/','https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/ZY24NNBBQNKVJINCRWWF267OBA.jpg?auth=05fe2fdf294f8d482fc1c8e37930590f1042db33e3dc1ef34d1d416c94c88dff&height=1005&width=1920&quality=80&smart=true','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-07 10:17:36','2026-07-12 14:27:54','2026-07-16 10:09:16'),(156,37,'Flavio Bolsonaro Battles U.S. Tariff Proposal Amid Brazilian Political Tensions','Flavio Bolsonaro, a Brazilian Senator and presidential candidate, voiced opposition to a proposed U.S. tariff on Brazilian goods. This effort aims to protect Brazil\'s economy and popular Pix payment system. As the U.S. Trade Representative considers the tariff, Bolsonaro positions himself against Brazil\'s leftist leadership, preparing for the upcoming election.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/politics/3946736-flavio-bol