-07-12 14:35:50','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(354,85,'The flawed case for slavery reparations','At a \"high-level United Nations consultative conference\" in Ghana earlier this month, African and Caribbean countries called on the countries that benefited from the transatlantic slave trade to make a formal apology and pay reparations to the descendants of the enslaved millions (or at least to the countries that the victims had come from).','Bangkok Post','https://www.bangkokpost.com/opinion/opinion/3274872/the-flawed-case-for-slavery-reparations','https://www.bangkokpost.com/v3/assets/images/img-default.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-22 10:13:00','2026-07-12 14:35:50','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(355,85,'Britain\'s economic woes fuel discontent with Brexit a decade after historic vote to leave EU','Simon Boyd’s firm makes prefabricated steel structures on the south coast of England and ships them to customers as far away as Ghana and Barbados. Mike Hawes represents Britain’s carmakers as the CEO of the Society of Motor Manufacturers and Traders. The business leaders were on different sides of the debate when Britain voted to leave the European Union in 2016. But 10 years later they are both frustrated by Brexit. A decade ago, backers promised that Brexit would be the key to a bright new future where, freed from the edicts of EU bureaucrats, Britain would regain control of its laws and its borders and the economy would boom.','The Atlanta Journal-Constitution','https://www.ajc.com/news/2026/06/britains-economic-woes-fuel-discontent-with-brexit-a-decade-after-historic-vote-to-leave-eu/','https://images.ajc.com/resizer/v2/OPT24GMV7NB45AKEY4D4MX54IM.jpg?auth=2a98c3375b338f41d60ee038017f2fe0cb441f5f96fea42b58dbd688fe8f6186&width=1200&height=630&smart=true','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-21 22:52:37','2026-07-12 14:35:50','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(356,85,'African and Caribbean leaders adopted a 19-point reparations plan in Ghana','African and Caribbean leaders adopted a 19-point reparations plan in Ghana demanding financial compensation, debt cancellation and apologies from slave trade beneficiaries.','Fox News','https://www.foxnews.com/world/african-caribbean-leaders-call-payments-debt-cancellation-formal-apologies-over-slavery','https://static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2026/06/ghana-president-mahama-ablakwa-conference-fox-news-001.jpeg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-20 19:10:02','2026-07-12 14:35:50','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(357,85,'African and Caribbean leaders urge former slave-trading nations to issue apologies and reparations','AFRICAN and Caribbean leaders in Ghana have urged former slave-trading nations to issue apologies and reparations over the trafficking of enslaved Africans after a landmark UN resolution in March declaring it “the gravest crime against humanity.”The Next Steps conference in the Ghanaian capital of Accra issued a declaration at the weekend calling on countries involved in the Atlantic slave trade to “offer full, formal and unconditional apologies as a foundational step towards reconciliation, trust-building and reparatory justice.”','The Morning Star','https://morningstaronline.co.uk/article/african-and-caribbean-leaders-urge-former-slave-trading-nations-issue-apologies-and','https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2026-06/AP26170739440902.jpg.webp?itok=Y90TyJeB','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-20 17:00:00','2026-07-12 14:35:50','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(358,92,'This $27 Wrap Dress Screams \'Rich Mom Vacationing in Greece\'','We found a coastal-inspired wrap dress that looks straight out of a Grecian boutique, and you can shop the look on sale with free shipping.','Us Weekly','https://www.usmagazine.com/shopping/news/flattering-coastal-inspired-wrap-dress/','https://www.usmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/wrap-dress.png?crop=0px%2C21px%2C1998px%2C1051px&resize=1200%2C630&quality=86&strip=all','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-12 02:15:01','2026-07-12 14:35:56','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(359,92,'LEPAS L8 Sets Sail for Six European Countries - Expanding in the Global NEV Market with Elegance','WUHU, China, July 08, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Recently, a shipment ceremony for LEPAS - Chery Group\'s all-new NEV brand rooted in an elegant lifestyle - was held at Wuhu Port. Nearly 1,500 units of the LEPAS L8 PHEV were loaded and set sail, destined for multiple European countries including Italy, Spain, Greece, Croatia, Slovenia, and Romania. This large-scale vehicle shipment marks a substantial step forward in LEPAS\'s \'Year of Delivery\', honoring its global commitments with the power of elegance.','The Manila Times','https://www.manilatimes.net/2026/07/09/tmt-newswire/globenewswire/lepas-l8-sets-sail-for-six-european-countries-expanding-in-the-global-nev-market-with-elegance/2381316','https://manilatimes.net/manilatimes/uploads/images/2026/07/09/1130500.jpg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-08 19:38:07','2026-07-12 14:35:57','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(360,92,'Economist: Exarchou: Greece Is Moving from Recovery to Self-Sustaining Growth','AKTOR Group Chairman and CEO Alexandros Exarchou argues that Greece has entered a new phase of economic maturity, where sustainable growth will increasingly depend on private investment, energy security and long-term competitiveness rather than extraordinary European support. Speaking at the 30th Annual Government Roundtable of The Economist, he outlined a vision of an economy capable of standing on its own foundations while positioning Greece as a strategic investment and energy hub for Europe. Economist: Exarchou: Greece Is Moving from Recovery to Self-Sustaining Growth','Pagenews.gr','https://www.pagenews.gr/2026/07/08/english-edition/economist-exarchou-greece-is-moving-from-recovery-to-self-sustaining-growth/','https://www.pagenews.gr/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/exarxou-1200x630.jpg','Logistics','Positive',5,0,'2026-07-08 06:26:09','2026-07-12 14:35:57','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(361,92,'Heidmar Maritime Holdings Corp. Expands Ship Management Platform','ATHENS, Greece and NEW YORK, July 07, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Heidmar Maritime Holdings Corp. (the \'Company” or \'Heidmar”) (NASDAQ: HMR) today announces that it has completed the acquisition of Q-Shipping B.V., a ship management and crewing business, adding nine vessels to its managed fleet and establishing an operating presence in the Netherlands and Turkey, with a dedicated crewing capability in Ukraine.','The Manila Times','https://www.manilatimes.net/2026/07/07/tmt-newswire/globenewswire/heidmar-maritime-holdings-corp-expands-ship-management-platform/2379777','https://manilatimes.net/manilatimes/uploads/images/2026/07/07/1127550.png','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-07 04:43:37','2026-07-12 14:35:57','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(362,92,'Vertical Corridor: Who secured capacity in the first long','The first major test of the new commercial model resulted in strong capacity commitments, new participants such as Metlen, and growing interest in Greece\'s natural gas export routes','Proto Thema','https://en.protothema.gr/2026/07/07/vertical-corridor-who-secured-capacity-in-the-first-long-term-auctions/','https://en.protothema.gr/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/lng1-2.jpg-2.jpg','Logistics','Positive',1,0,'2026-07-06 23:22:44','2026-07-12 14:35:57','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(363,92,'Atlantic See Strengthens Position in Vertical Gas Corridor,Reinforcing Greece\'s Role as Regional Energy Hub','The DEPA Commercial–AKTOR Group joint venture secured 13,000 MWh of daily capacity in the first annual auction under the new Vertical Gas Corridor commercial framework, marking a significant step toward strengthening Southeast Europe\'s energy security and expanding LNG trade across the region. Atlantic See Strengthens Position in Vertical Gas Corridor,Reinforcing Greece\'s Role as Regional Energy Hub','Pagenews.gr','https://www.pagenews.gr/2026/07/06/english-edition/atlantic-see-strengthens-position-in-vertical-gas-corridorreinforcing