s Indo-Pacific Ties','BJP MP Sambit Patra lauds PM Modi\'s strategic visits to Indonesia, Australia, New Zealand, and Seychelles, emphasizing enhanced partnerships in defense, economy, and culture. These initiatives fortify India\'s position across the Indo-Pacific and Indian Ocean regions, aligning with nations like Japan and Australia to advance national interests.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/headlines/3949036-das-kadam-das-ka-dam-strengthening-indias-indo-pacific-ties','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/devnews/12_07_2026_13_48_05_4232527.jpg&width=920&format=jpeg','Economy','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-12 01:18:10','2026-07-14 04:09:20','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(500,120,'Charting the global economy: Iran war continues to cloud outlook','Japan\'s bank lending expansion suggests room for the central bank to raise rates further. Meanwhile, high borrowing costs continue to impact the US housing market significantly.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/trade/exports/insights/charting-the-global-economy-iran-war-continues-to-cloud-outlook/articleshow/132340595.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132340610,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-120816,overlay-etrise/articleshow.jpg','Economy','Negative',0,1,'2026-07-11 21:35:00','2026-07-14 04:09:20','2026-07-16 10:09:17'),(501,120,'Japan wants 60 million tourists, but China isn’t sending them','Tokyo is banking on a massive visitor boom to do what its factories and financiers increasingly cannot: carry the economy forward.','South China Morning Post','https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/economics/article/3360158/japan-wants-60-million-tourists-china-isnt-sending-them','https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/og_image_scmp_generic/public/d8/images/canvas/2026/07/10/dde47663-f38e-4af1-b931-048664b676dc_35d9e0a6.jpg?itok=jWkbCwq4&v=1783682101','Economy','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-11 18:45:05','2026-07-14 04:09:20','2026-07-1