ruary 28.','BreakingNews.ie','https://www.breakingnews.ie/world/us-strikes-iran-again-as-it-tries-to-limit-attacks-on-ships-in-strait-of-hormuz-1925656.html','https://img.resized.co/breaking-news/eyJkYXRhIjoie1widXJsXCI6XCJodHRwczpcXFwvXFxcL2ltYWdlcy5icmVha2luZ25ld3MuaWVcXFwvcHJvZFxcXC91cGxvYWRzXFxcLzIwMjZcXFwvMDdcXFwvMTIxMzUzMTdcXFwvYTcyM2Q2Y2Y0NGU5NDkyM2EwOWNkYTI1ZDkwZWVkZDUtMTMuanBnXCIsXCJ3aWR0aFwiOjEyMDAsXC','Logistics','Negative',0,14,'2026-07-12 13:17:39','2026-07-14 04:16:42','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(727,178,'NIA chargesheets Pakistan terrorist Shehzad Bhatti among 8 in Ambala police station blast case','Pakistani terrorist had established operational modules in India and assigned local operatives to arrange logistics and explosive substances for carrying out attacks at police establishments as part of the conspiracy, as per NIA’s findings','The Tribune','https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/india/nia-chargesheets-pakistan-terrorist-shehzad-bhatti-among-8-in-ambala-police-station-blast-case/','https://www.tribuneindia.com/sortd-service/imaginary/v22-01/jpg/large/high?url=dGhldHJpYnVuZS1zb3J0ZC1wcm8tcHJvZC1zb3J0ZC9tZWRpYWUxNTUxOTgwLTdkMzctMTFmMS1hZmFlLTJkNzNlMTMwYzExYi5qcGc=','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-11 07:50:28','2026-07-14 04:16:42','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(728,178,'Pakistan stocks fall 1.74% in weekly trade amid US-Iran tensions','KARACHI: The Pakistan Stock Exchange (PSX) ended the week in negative territory, with the benchmark KSE-100 Index declining 1.74% as','BOL News','https://www.bolnews.com/business/pakistan-stocks-fall-1-74-in-weekly-trade-amid-us-iran-tensions/','https://www.bolnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/FotoJet-48.webp','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-11 05:51:40','2026-07-14 04:16:42','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(729,178,'British MP Rupert Lowe unveils hardline Pakistan policy as Islamabad refuses to accept Shabir Ahmed\'s deportation','UK News: British MP Rupert Lowe proposes a hardline policy towards Pakistan after the country\'s refusa