nces consultation on new bill as it steps up policies regarding ‘unlawful’ Israeli activities.','Al Jazeera','https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/6/19/norway-seeks-to-ban-trade-with-illegal-israeli-settlements-in-palestine','https://www.aljazeera.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ap_6a35748236ede-1781888130.jpg?resize=1920%2C1440','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-19 12:18:35','2026-07-14 04:18:13','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(733,190,'Unison to lobby for complete trade ban with illegal West Bank settlements','UNISON will lobby Labour for a complete ban on trade with illegal settlements on the occupied West Bank, its conference moved today.Delegates in Brighton criticised the government for failing to strongly demand the Israeli government comply with international law after recognising the state of Palestine in September.They passed a motion for Unison to lobby the government to introduce a legal ban on trade with the illegal settlements and suspend the British-Israeli arms trade “until international and human rights law are respected.”','The Morning Star','https://morningstaronline.co.uk/article/unison-lobby-complete-trade-ban-illegal-west-bank-settlements','https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2026-06/AP26168454968752.jpg.webp?itok=zT8FVyxW','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-17 17:00:00','2026-07-14 04:18:13','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(734,190,'Settler products from occupied Palestine sold to Europe as Israeli, investigation finds','Shipments deliberately mislabelled to bolster settler economy, says non-profit Global Echo','The Guardian','https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/jun/15/settler-products-from-occupied-palestine-sold-to-europe-as-israeli-investigation-finds','https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/361d37c31be226658b48478188ffc74e6e26abf2/920_0_5200_4160/master/5200.jpg?width=1200&height=630&quality=85&auto=format&fit=crop&precrop=40:21,offset-x50,offset-y0&overlay-align=bottom%2Cleft&overlay-width=100p&overlay-base64=','Economy','Positive',1,