illion emerging market equity exodus in June','A sharp retreat from tech-heavy equities in South Korea and Taiwan fuelled net emerging market stock outflows of $46.1 billion from foreign investor ​portfolios in June, banking trade group data showed, contributing to a second ‌straight month of overall portfolio losses for developing economies.','Reuters','https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-taiwan-lead-46-billion-emerging-market-equity-exodus-june-2026-07-10/','https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/XNXJ4ZK5CJJEJCUKDKBNGBCQBQ.jpg?auth=5c680bbbc05865d7c1694832971b297a5e3db8e101a1f0689a7fdc5bd77472ba&height=1005&width=1920&quality=80&smart=true','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-10 07:04:12','2026-07-16 09:54:48','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(901,127,'Revanth Reddy Targets BRS, Urges Opposition to Let the Government Do Its Job','Revanth Reddy said the state government envisioned making Telangana compete with countries such as South Korea and China and transforming the state into a $3 trillion economy by 2047.','Deccan Chronicle','https://www.deccanchronicle.com/southern-states/telangana/revanth-reddy-targets-brs-urges-opposition-to-let-the-government-do-its-job-1969726','https://www.deccanchronicle.com/h-upload/2026/07/09/2061930-cm-revanth.jpg','Economy','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-09 12:42:19','2026-07-16 09:54:48','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(902,72,'World Cup Security, NFL Suspensions, and MLB Trades: A Busy Week in Sports','The sports world sees increased security in Atlanta for the England-Argentina World Cup semi-final, an NFL suspension for Cowboys\' Charles Snowden, and an MLB trade involving Lance McCullers Jr. The Detroit Red Wings see a shift in management while Spain\'s soccer team dominates France, reaching the World Cup final.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/sports-games/3950884-world-cup-security-nfl-suspensions-and-mlb-trades-a-busy-week-in-sports','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/aiimagegallery/18_08_2025_11_31_06_9035495.png&width=920&format=jpeg','Logistics','Positive',1,0,'2026-07-15 09:56:49','2026-07-16 09:55:54','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(903,72,'Food Fables - The other time Cabo Verde influenced the world','Before its World Cup exit against Argentina, Cabo Verde emerged as one of the tournament\'s biggest surprises, drawing attention to its rich Portuguese heritage and little-known historical ties with Goa. The island nation played a crucial role in Portugal\'s maritime expansion during the Age of Discovery, serving as a strategic stopover for explorers, trade, and later the transatlantic slave trade. Cabo Verde\'s diverse culture, cuisine and traditions reflect centuries of global exchange, while its geopolitical significance peaked with the 1494 Treaty of Tordesillas, which divided newly discovered lands between Portugal and Spain.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/food-fables-the-other-time-cabo-verde-influenced-the-world/articleshow/132414188.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132414581,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-129496,overlay-etpanache/articleshow.jpg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-15 04:22:00','2026-07-16 09:55:54','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(904,72,'Sports Drama: Transfers, Suspensions, and World Cup Tensions','Current sports news highlights include Atlanta United signing Chile\'s Paulo Diaz, enhanced security for the England-Argentina World Cup semi-final, Charles Snowden\'s NFL suspension, and the Red Sox\'s trade with the Tigers for Jahmai Jones. Other notable events involve Chicago Bears\' stadium plans, controversies over FIFA rulings, and Spain\'s World Cup triumph.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/sports-games/3950527-sports-drama-transfers-suspensions-and-world-cup-tensions','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/aiimagegallery/15_08_2025_05_02_36_5210998.png&width=920&format=jpeg','Logistics','Neutra