,0,0,'2026-07-14 15:56:27','2026-07-16 09:55:54','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(908,72,'Gibraltar ushers in a new era as British territory\'s border fence with Spain is removed','The fence separating Gibraltar from Spain has been dismantled, easing travel for thousands who cross daily. This change follows years of post-Brexit negotiations between the EU and the UK over Gibraltar, a British Overseas Territory that is also claimed by Spain. On Tuesday, the UK and EU signed an agreement securing Gibraltar’s economic future. Without it, Gibraltar could have faced a hard border with full passport checks, risking its economy. The deal de facto brings Gibraltar into the EU’s Schengen free travel area. Gibraltar officials say live facial recognition cameras are now set up at entry points.','The Atlanta Journal-Constitution','https://www.ajc.com/news/2026/07/gibraltar-ushers-in-a-new-era-as-british-territorys-border-fence-with-spain-is-removed/','https://images.ajc.com/resizer/v2/KIRU7YI4ZRHGJMOK2AE5R2O7OA.jpg?auth=0b7bb56eb355f8277868158a41d64bffcc127ea363d2d5c00c9bf561f5eadeca&width=1200&height=630&smart=true','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-14 15:22:39','2026-07-16 09:55:54','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(909,72,'Chandigarh Administration moves Centre, registers FIR to stall heritage furniture auctions in US, Spain','The Chandigarh Administration has written to the Ministry of External Affairs (MEA) seeking urgent diplomatic intervention to stall two overseas auctions of Pierre Jeanneret-designed heritage furniture from the city’s Capitol Project — one in Los Angeles on July 15 and the other in Barcelona, Spain, on July 22. An FIR has been registered in connection with the suspected theft and illegal export of the pieces, replicating the legal and diplomatic framework that successfully halted the Paris auction last month.','The Tribune','https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/chandigarh/chandigarh-administration-moves-centre-registers-fir-to-stall-heritage-furniture-auctions-in-us-spain/