ia\'s health, and Brazil contends with EU export rules.','Devdiscourse','https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/health/3945252-health-news-briefs-anesthesia-concerns-ebola-innovations-and-global-health-challenges','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/aiimagegallery/18_09_2025_10_18_37_5845231.png&width=920&format=jpeg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-04 05:58:21','2026-07-16 09:57:25','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(970,235,'Against all odds, one of nature’s most colorful little survivors just made an incredible return','A vibrant blue gecko, once threatened by the pet trade and habitat loss, is making a remarkable comeback in Tanzania. Conservation efforts, including trade restrictions, captive breeding, and crucial habitat restoration by local communities, have revitalized the species\' dwindling population. This success story highlights how focused conservation, even for a small creature with a limited range, can protect an entire ecosystem.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/us/against-all-odds-one-of-natures-most-colorful-little-survivors-just-made-an-incredible-return/articleshow/132073370.cms','https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-132073370,width-1200,height-630,imgsize-19443,overlay-economictimes/articleshow.jpg','Trade','Neutral',0,0,'2026-06-29 07:55:00','2026-07-16 09:57:25','2026-07-16 10:09:18'),(971,235,'From Oman to Tanzania: How the Iran war is redrawing India’s trade map','India\'s trade is changing due to West Asia conflict. Oman is now a major import partner, especially for energy. Russia and the US are also key import sources. Singapore has become India\'s third-largest export destination. Tanzania and South Africa are seeing increased Indian exports. These shifts highlight new trade routes and partnerships.','The Economic Times','https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/foreign-trade/from-oman-to-tanzania-how-the-iran-war-is-redrawing-indias-trade-map/arti