s-textile-industry','https://www.devdiscourse.com/img?imageUrl=https://devdiscourse.blob.core.windows.net/devnews/15_07_2026_17_58_54_66416.jpg&width=920&format=jpeg','Logistics','Neutral',0,0,'2026-07-15 05:29:01','2026-07-16 10:08:16','2026-07-16 10:09:19'),(1086,247,'UK trade deal to help India compete with Bangladesh, Vietnam; create jobs: Traders','The India-UK Free Trade Agreement (FTA) is expected to provide a much-needed boost to Surat\'s textile and garment industry by improving export competitiveness, generating employment and helping Indian manufacturers compete more effectively with rivals such as Bangladesh and Vietnam, local industry representatives said.','The Tribune','https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/business/india-uk-trade-deal-to-help-india-compete-with-bangladesh-vietnam-create-jobs-traders/','https://www.tribuneindia.com/sortd-service/imaginary/v22-01/jpg/large/high?url=dGhldHJpYnVuZS1zb3J0ZC1wcm8tcHJvZC1zb3J0ZC9tZWRpYWE4NWMyZGQwLTgwNDgtMTFmMS1hMjIxLWM3MTFjYjk5YTdlZS5qcGc=','Logistics','Positive',1,0,'2026-07-15 05:28:10','2026-07-16 10:08:16','2026-07-16 10:09:19'),(1087,247,'Why four Asian countries got a World Bank income upgrade-and India didn’t','India has remained stuck in the lower-middle-income group as Vietnam and the Philippines have moved up. The gap exposes the harder challenge facing the world\'s fastest-growing major economy: turning aggregate growth into higher incomes.','Livemint','https://www.livemint.com/economy/india-growth-story-world-bank-income-classification-vietnam-philippines-11784093261774.html','https://www.livemint.com/lm-img/img/2026/07/15/1600x900/logo/FILES-US-WORLDBANK-ECONOMY-INDICATOR-GROWTH-0_1718121885994_1784098523460_37086322-e879-4e60-9827-4a6380ca4500.jpg','Economy','Positive',1,0,'2026-07-15 00:04:10','2026-07-16 10:08:16','2026-07-16 10:09:19'),(1088,247,'Tragic Capsizing Claims Lives of Indian Tourists in Vietnam','The bodies of AC Thomas and Loveni Thomas, who died in a Vietnam speedboat accident, are